      "question": "How do I get started with Nexa Manager?",
      "answer": "To get started with Nexa Manager, register for an account, complete your company profile, and follow the initial setup guide. Our support team is available for personalized assistance."
    },
    "q2": {
      "question": "How can I manage my clients?",
      "answer": "Go to the Clients section to add, edit, and organize your client information. You can import existing contacts or add new ones manually."
    },
    "q3": {
      "question": "How to create and send invoices?",
      "answer": "In the Invoices section, click 'New Invoice', fill in the client and service details, customize the design, and send it directly via email or download as a PDF."
    },
    "q4": {
      "question": "Is it possible to integrate Nexa Manager with other software?",
      "answer": "Yes, Nexa Manager offers APIs and integrations with major accounting software, CRMs, and payment systems. Check the API documentation for more details."
    },
    "q5": {
      "question": "How can I access financial reports?",
      "answer": "Reports are available in the Analytics section. You can generate custom reports for revenue, expenses, clients, and business performance with filters for period and category."
